# MorphoWrite

## Setup

python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

## Run locally

./run_dev.sh or make dev

App:
http://localhost:8080

## Stop

./stop_dev.sh or make stop

## Static files
Uses Tailwind CDN for development, no config.
DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=config.settings.production python manage.py collectstatic